{"data":{"index":1,"total":1,"posts":[{"title":"IPhone抓包调试神器—Stream使用方法介绍","slug":"常用工具/IPhone抓包调试神器—Stream使用方法介绍","date":"2024-02-11T00:24:09.763Z","updated":"2025-10-28T09:44:06.586Z","comments":true,"url":"posts/fa619435/","excerpt":"<html><head></head><body><p>写过爬虫的同学都知道，当我们想对App或者小程序进行抓包时，最常用的工具是Charles、Fiddler或者MimtProxy。但这些软件用起来非常复杂。今天介绍一款ios端的抓包调试神器-Stream。Stream是一款免费轻量级移动端ios抓包调试工具，配置方便无需设置代理，集成了HTTP抓包、构建请求、Hosts 设置、常用工具、数据导出等功能。</p>\n<p>Stream可以直接在app store中进行下载：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211082234652.png\" alt=\"image-20240211082234652\"></p>\n<p>下载后打开Stream，会弹出添加VPN配置，选择“允许”，并下载CA证书。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211082403880.png\" alt=\"image-20240211082403880\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211082433496.png\" alt=\"image-20240211082433496\"></p>\n<p>记得一定要在“设置”-“通用”-“关于本机-证书信任设置”，开启信任。这步如果不做的话，报文会抓取不到。平时如果用不到，可以像我这样将其关闭。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211083132851.png\" alt=\"image-20240211083132851\"></p>\n<p>现在回到stream软件首页，点击“设置抓包模式”，然后“开启白名单模式”，比如我们想抓京东的包，可以把“api.m.jd.com”添加到白名单里面，然后点击“立即生效”，stream软件设置完成。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211083158402.png\" alt=\"image-20240211083158402\"></p>\n<p>现在回到Steam软件首页，点击“开始抓包”，然后保持stream软件后台运行，打开京东APP，进我的页面下拉刷新几下页面状态，或者去购物车随便点击几个自己加入到购物车的商品。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211083344899.png\" alt=\"image-20240211083344899\"></p>\n<p>然后回到Stream，点击『停止抓包』按钮。抓包过程就完成了。</p>\n<p>我们点击『抓包历史』按钮，找到刚刚抓到的数据包，如下图所示：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211083427592.png\" alt=\"image-20240211083427592\"></p>\n<p>如果电脑上有Chales等工具，可以导出HAR发送到电脑中进行查看。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211083718492.png\" alt=\"image-20240211083718492\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211083929990.png\" alt=\"image-20240211083929990\"></p>\n</body></html>","cover":"https://wechat-2025-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/file-20251028174209087.png","images":["https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211082234652.png","https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211082403880.png","https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211082433496.png","https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211083132851.png","https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211083158402.png","https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211083344899.png","https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211083427592.png","https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211083718492.png","https://wechat-public-1258175280.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/images/2023-12/image-20240211083929990.png"],"categories":[{"name":"常用工具","slug":"常用工具","api":"api/categories/常用工具.json"}],"tags":[],"api":"api/posts/posts/fa619435.json"}],"info":{"type":"archive","year":2024,"month":2}},"api":"api/archives/2024/02/page.1.json"}